{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-blog-tsx","path":"/blog/","result":{"data":{"allMdx":{"edges":[{"node":{"timeToRead":10,"frontmatter":{"slug":"/blog/a-year-into-learning-japanese/","title":"A year into learning Japanese","date":"2021-05-06","dateFormatted":"6th May 2021","excerpt":"<p>It‚Äôs been just over a year since I started learning Japanese so I thought it was a good time to stop, reflect over my journey and consider what I‚Äôve learnt. I started on 19th April 2020 and since then I‚Äôve dedicated 1,378 hours to studying (according to my timer app). That‚Äôs just over 25 hours a week, which is quite a lot on top of a full time job. In this post, I will try to justify to myself how I spent that much time on a single hobby (neglecting everything else in my life) as well as point people to the resources I used (in case it helps anyone)...</p>","imageAlt":"","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.6260162601626016,"src":"/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/ee604/time-allocation-pie-chart.png","srcSet":"/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/69585/time-allocation-pie-chart.png 200w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/497c6/time-allocation-pie-chart.png 400w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/ee604/time-allocation-pie-chart.png 800w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/8f331/time-allocation-pie-chart.png 820w","srcWebp":"/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/58556/time-allocation-pie-chart.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/61e93/time-allocation-pie-chart.webp 200w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/1f5c5/time-allocation-pie-chart.webp 400w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/58556/time-allocation-pie-chart.webp 800w,\n/static/38a4172ed53b1264d4e88907e7e6edc9/b1a18/time-allocation-pie-chart.webp 820w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}},{"node":{"timeToRead":8,"frontmatter":{"slug":"/blog/how-i-felt-about-inheriting-200000/","title":"How I felt about inheriting ¬£200,000","date":"2021-03-01","dateFormatted":"1st March 2021","excerpt":"<p>People don‚Äôt like to talk about money, much less money that‚Äôs inherited. But as much as it is an extremely privileged situation to be in, there‚Äôs a bunch of feelings to disentangle when you inherit a large sum of money. Especially if you‚Äôre not used to it and don‚Äôt come from a wealthy background. You have to navigate the grief you have for the person who has died, guilt for benefiting from their death, and anxiety over what to do with it all.</p> <p>If you want resources, there are countless articles that explain the administrative process of what to do when someone dies. And there are many other dry personal finance articles that assume you want to maximise your return on your inheritance money. But I couldn‚Äôt find much out there that touch on the emotional side of inheritance. So that‚Äôs why I want to break the silence and describe the journey I went through. I also ended up doing something a bit unusual and not often talked about...</p>","imageAlt":"A statue of a person curled up with their head in their knees.","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/14b42/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/f836f/cover.jpg 200w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/2244e/cover.jpg 400w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/14b42/cover.jpg 800w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/47498/cover.jpg 1200w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/e720d/cover.jpg 1267w","srcWebp":"/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/58556/cover.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/61e93/cover.webp 200w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/1f5c5/cover.webp 400w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/58556/cover.webp 800w,\n/static/6c0c691e8f3394c91502d4509960d94a/99238/cover.webp 1200w,\n/static/6c0c